StringValues.16: A note from Mara al Luq outside Yaraq, for delivery to Nasur ibn Tifar in the North Yaraq Outpost.
StringValues.15: A note from Mara al Luq for delivery to Nasun ibn Tifar.

Pages.Text:
Dearest Nasun,

I was delighted to receive your kind words.  Pray, do bring such a thing yourself next time, that I may read it by your side at the reflecting pool.

- Mara
